-- Liepajas Metalurgs Submits Legal Protection Request to Court
-- B y   A a r o n   E g l i t i s
-- 2013-05-27T07:15:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-27/liepajas-metalurgs-submits-legal-protection-request-to-court.html
Liepajas Metalurgs AS, a Latvian
steelmaker that has asked for government help, filed a request
for legal protection in a local court on May 24, the company
said in a statement to the stock exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aaron Eglitis in Riga at 
